raw_data.releaseNotes:
hey there! we are so excited to bring you this update:

– we added autumn stickers pt. 2 to keep the cozy vibes going;
– we added project titles so you can name your projects clearly;
– now you can add and remove frames in template-based projects for more creative flexibility;
– we redesigned layer selection for a cleaner, more intuitive feel;
– as usual, we fixed a lot of things and made the app run smoother than ever.

feel free to hit us up at hello@17v28.app or via our socials @17v28.app

enjoy the app!

apps.description:
THU is a global organization that relies on a curated community where like-minded creative talents, business agents, and governmental partners exchange knowledge, inspiration, and opportunities to impact society through the development of the creative economy.

Access the latest version of our THU platform app, now available all year long, and get ready to:

- Apply to opportunities and engage with mentors, companies and industry giants;
- Collaborate on exciting new projects;
- Showcase your skills and exchange knowledge and inspiration;
- Access exclusive content;
- Connect with creatives worldwide;
- Access our events’ schedule and unlock new features now available on mobile!

Join our worldwide community of thousands of creative doers, thinkers and change-makers
and start experiencing THU 365 days a year, anywhere and anytime, an all-in-one platform for the Creative Industries.

